item.title: How to change att str def lvl [DELTA]
item.dc:creator: @OwnageDBOW OwnageDBOW
item.description:
@OwnageDBOW wrote:

Go to your character files and look for the account you want to edit. You should see this towards the end

[SKILLS] character-skill = 0 99 29302500 character-skill = 1 99 28000000 character-skill = 2 99 14000100 character-skill = 3 99 14459401 character-skill = 4 99 14000000 character-skill = 5 72 28001980 character-skill = 6 99 28000000 character-skill = 7 99 28000000 character-skill = 8 99 28000000 character-skill = 9 99 28000000 character-skill = 10 99 28000000 character-skill = 11 99 28000000 character-skill = 12 99 28000000 character-skill = 13 99 28020000 character-skill = 14 99 28001220 character-skill = 15 99 28000000 character-skill = 16 99 28000000 character-skill = 17 99 28000000 character-skill = 18 99 28000000 character-skill = 19 99 28000000 character-skill = 20 99 28000000 character-skill = 21 1 0 character-skill = 22 1 0 character-skill = 23 1 0 character-skill = 24 1 0

Edit the first 7 for attack, strength, defence, magic, ranged, hitpoints, and prayer. I do not remember the order. If you want 1 strength do this. (Might be wrong.)

character-skill = 1 1 0
You must also edit the EXP.
